    {
      "id": "https://myjetpack.tumblr.com/post/815685763747414016",
      "url": "https://myjetpack.tumblr.com/post/815685763747414016",
      "title": "My latest cartoon for New Scientist. ",
      "content_html": "<img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/385ea4a2f23ac68a90ff0d34ddc16c27/3b69dd1d158fa7ea-50/s640x960/4371cb5c6f4ad1ff1ec4e8a1ae167caa4feeed4d.jpg\" data-orig-height=\"1035\" data-orig-width=\"1500\" alt=\"Puzzle time! &#10;&#10;Image: A stick figure stands before a complicated machine. Flames rise from part of it with containers labelled Lava, Water and Oil above. Tangled ropes lead from the containers to handles labelled A, B, and C.&#10;&#10;Caption: Professor Mulligan&#xE2;&#x80;&#x99;s apparatus has caught fire! Should you pull rope A, B, C, or schedule a meeting with HR to discuss the professor&#xE2;&#x80;&#x99;s increasingly deranged experiments?\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/385ea4a2f23ac68a90ff0d34ddc16c27/3b69dd1d158fa7ea-50/s75x75_c1/177bb6d48a5559125d8d8ab4d4bf39d2b3af05cb.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/385ea4a2f23ac68a90ff0d34ddc16c27/3b69dd1d158fa7ea-50/s100x200/50b81a046c30cbf3eb556c37d816ca09a67e3512.jpg 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/385ea4a2f23ac68a90ff0d34ddc16c27/3b69dd1d158fa7ea-50/s250x400/90054b37d12de2281554195a2f0fd2896ef357d3.jpg 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/385ea4a2f23ac68a90ff0d34ddc16c27/3b69dd1d158fa7ea-50/s400x600/7a376becea98c1d341ad2460dc8bc51d2b64df7d.jpg 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/385ea4a2f23ac68a90ff0d34ddc16c27/3b69dd1d158fa7ea-50/s500x750/04c6bee88d864bd654a6e2a11cacfab9b990287e.jpg 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/385ea4a2f23ac68a90ff0d34ddc16c27/3b69dd1d158fa7ea-50/s540x810/5230ba40c42c322cf750d1fdd04fa5990919a8cb.jpg 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/385ea4a2f23ac68a90ff0d34ddc16c27/3b69dd1d158fa7ea-50/s640x960/4371cb5c6f4ad1ff1ec4e8a1ae167caa4feeed4d.jpg 640w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/385ea4a2f23ac68a90ff0d34ddc16c27/3b69dd1d158fa7ea-50/s1280x1920/4639127490c207dcb5f5dcff18517fe0e892b426.jpg 1280w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/385ea4a2f23ac68a90ff0d34ddc16c27/3b69dd1d158fa7ea-50/s2048x3072/4f25fa9f5e3815496a445d36e7bc537f6966cf99.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\"/>"
